text:
Located directly opposite the carpark at Joo Chiat Road / Tembling Road Open Space Carpark & the ‘Bef Joo Chiat Pl’ bus stop.

A minimart that has a great variety of
- soft drinks, milk, juice, hot drinks
- toiletries e.g., shampoo, body wash, detergent, soap, toothbrushes and more
- snacks e.g., potato chips, snack bars, biscuits.

Offers A4 B&W printing services.

Friendly store owners with helpful personalities.
Not close to any public transportation station
